For better performance, consider creating a `characterMap` using `useMemo`. This avoids repeated O(n) `find` operations within the party list rendering loop, which can become a bottleneck as the number of characters and parties grows.

```
  const characterMap = useMemo(
    () => new Map(characters.map(c => [c.id, c])),
    [characters]
  );

```

