Pass the `acNote` property to the `CharacterMiniSummary` component to ensure any specific AC details (like 'natural armor' or 'shield') are displayed.

```
                                        maxHp={character.maxHp}
                                        acNote={character.acNote}
```

![medium](https://www.gstatic.com/codereviewagent/medium-priority.svg)

Add `acNote` to the component props to support displaying additional AC context, which is common in D&D stat blocks.

```suggestion
interface CharacterMiniSummaryProps {
  name: string;
  race?: string;
  characterType?: CharacterType;
  classes?: CharacterClass[];
  ac: number;
  acNote?: string;
  hp: number;
  maxHp: number;
}
```
